title: KMFDM Studio Album Discography (AAC/M4A)
description:
This is the complete Studio Album discography for KMFDM, none of the side projects, remix albums or other albums are here. If you want those they are not too difficult to find. 

I took FLAC downloads I collected and converted them to aac/m4a files at maximum variable bit rate using the Fraunhofer FDK AAC codec library, which is the best open source solution available. 

Why AAC? Simply put, it's because its time for people to start uploading music with a modern codec instead of in the antiquated MP3 format. All modern players support the m4a/aac standard and should pose no problem for listeners.

The albums are sorted by both file names and directories, and with proper ID3 tags. Album info for year is different from the official release date for all the remastered albums included within this torrent.

Included albums:

[1992] Money
[1993] Angst
[1993] Don't Blow Your Top
[1997] [symbols]
[2002] Attak
[2002] Opium 1984
[2003] WWIII
[2005] Hau Ruck
[2006] Naive
[2006] What Do You Know, Deutschland?
[2007] Adios
[2007] Nihil
[2007] UAIOE
[2007] Xtort
[2008] Tohuvabohu
[2009] Blitz
[2011] WTF?!
[2013] Kunst
[2014] Our Time Will Come
